## Paradigm Challenge Tracking

Tracks when paradigm challenge phases run during scheduled reviews (every 4th run). Prevents local-optima convergence by periodically questioning the PE architecture.

| Date | Scheduled review # | Challenge ran? | Key findings | Action taken |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| — | 0 | — | _No scheduled reviews recorded yet_ | — |

**Next paradigm challenge due at**: scheduled review #4

